<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="371" type="comments">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="371">Comments.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="371">This species has recently been described from the Nyungwe National Park in southwestern Rwanda, and it is one of the few species with broad distributions; however, this is a new distributional record. The male genitalia are identical to the illustrations provided in the original description.</paragraph>
